This project focuses on improving professional communication skills through email writing and responsible social media use. I drafted two formal emails—one to a professor requesting an extension and another to an internship coordinator—following proper email etiquette such as clear subject lines, professional tone, and structured format.

I also created a checklist of social media Do’s and Don’ts to promote responsible online behavior. Additionally, I reflected on the importance of clear and professional digital communication.

Overall, this task helped me develop effective communication skills for academic and professional environments.
